{
  "title": "Wield — Skill Usage",
  "uid": "wield-skill-usage",
  "tags": ["wield", "phase-1"],
  "description": "Phase 1 disposable dashboard (ADR-0002): usage metrics joined at query time against the skill_meta info metrics pushed by CI (docs/delivery.md). Every group_left join wraps the map side in topk+last_over_time — see the join notes panel.",
  "editable": true,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "time": { "from": "now-7d", "to": "now" },
  "refresh": "",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "label": "Data source",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "refresh": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "user",
        "label": "Person",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total, user_email)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total, user_email)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": { "selected": true, "text": ["All"], "value": ["$__all"] },
        "sort": 1
      },
      {
        "name": "category",
        "label": "Category",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
        "query": {
          "query": "label_values(skill_meta{job=\"wield\"}, category)",
          "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(skill_meta{job=\"wield\"}, category)",
        "refresh": 2,
        "multi": true,
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": { "selected": true, "text": ["All"], "value": ["$__all"] },
        "sort": 1
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Overall usage",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tracked skills in map",
      "description": "Distinct skills currently in the pushed metadata map (25h last_over_time window). Zero means the CI push has not delivered, or the daily cron lapsed — see docs/delivery.md.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "count(topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\"}[25h])))",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Join notes",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Usage metrics join the metadata map at query time (ADR-0002).\n\nEvery `group_left` join wraps the map side as\n`topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta[25h]))`\n— drop the wrapper and the panel errors with *found duplicate series* for up to a day after any skill's metadata changes.\n\nDetails: `docs/delivery.md`."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Top skills by tokens",
      "description": "All skills, tracked or not, ranked by token usage over the dashboard time range.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 10, "x": 4, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "continuous-BlPu" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "valueMode": "color",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "namePlacement": "auto",
        "sizing": "auto",
        "minVizHeight": 16,
        "minVizWidth": 8,
        "maxVizHeight": 300
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "topk(15, sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{skill_name}}",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "bargauge",
      "title": "Top skills by cost",
      "description": "All skills, tracked or not, ranked by cost over the dashboard time range.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 10, "x": 14, "y": 1 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "color": { "mode": "continuous-YlRd" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "displayMode": "gradient",
        "valueMode": "color",
        "showUnfilled": true,
        "namePlacement": "auto",
        "sizing": "auto",
        "minVizHeight": 16,
        "minVizWidth": 8,
        "maxVizHeight": 300
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "topk(15, sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{skill_name}}",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "By dimension",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "piechart",
      "title": "Tokens by category",
      "description": "Grouping dimension `category` partitions tracked skills; the (untracked) slice is usage by skills absent from the metadata map.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "pieType": "pie",
        "displayLabels": ["name"],
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true,
          "values": ["percent"]
        },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (category) (sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])) * on(skill_name) group_left(category) topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\", category=~\"${category:regex}\"}[25h])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{category}}",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])) unless on(skill_name) last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\"}[25h]))",
          "legendFormat": "(untracked)",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Tracked skills — dimensions, tokens, cost",
      "description": "One row per tracked skill with its category, joined against usage over the dashboard time range. Untracked skills appear only in the overall panels.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 16, "x": 8, "y": 12 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          },
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "cellOptions": { "type": "auto" }, "filterable": true }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "Cost" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "unit", "value": "currencyUSD" }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Tokens", "desc": true }],
        "footer": { "show": false, "reducer": ["sum"], "fields": "" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (skill_name, category) (sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])) * on(skill_name) group_left(category) topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\", category=~\"${category:regex}\"}[25h])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (skill_name, category) (sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])) * on(skill_name) group_left(category) topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\", category=~\"${category:regex}\"}[25h])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        { "id": "merge", "options": {} },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true },
            "indexByName": {},
            "renameByName": {
              "skill_name": "Skill",
              "category": "Category",
              "Value #A": "Tokens",
              "Value #B": "Cost"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Per person",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Tokens by person × skill",
      "description": "All skills, tracked or not. Consent note (docs/consent.md): per-person numbers are for learning, never performance review.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          },
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "cellOptions": { "type": "auto" }, "filterable": true }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "Tokens", "desc": true }],
        "footer": { "show": false, "reducer": ["sum"], "fields": "" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (user_email, skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range]))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true },
            "indexByName": {},
            "renameByName": {
              "user_email": "Person",
              "skill_name": "Skill",
              "Value": "Tokens"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Tokens by person × category",
      "description": "Tracked skills only — the matrix cell is tokens spent by that person in that category over the dashboard time range.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 23 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }]
          },
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "cellOptions": { "type": "auto" }, "filterable": true }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [],
        "footer": { "show": false, "reducer": ["sum"], "fields": "" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (user_email, category) (sum by (user_email, skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__range])) * on(skill_name) group_left(category) topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\", category=~\"${category:regex}\"}[25h])))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "range": false
        }
      ],
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "groupingToMatrix",
          "options": {
            "columnField": "category",
            "rowField": "user_email",
            "valueField": "Value",
            "emptyValue": "null"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": {},
            "indexByName": {},
            "renameByName": { "user_email\\category": "Person" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Trend",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Token usage over time by skill",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 34 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true, "calcs": [] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{skill_name}}",
          "range": true,
          "instant": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cost over time by category",
      "description": "Tracked skills grouped by category; (untracked) is everything absent from the metadata map.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 34 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "barAlignment": 0,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true, "calcs": [] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (category) (sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval])) * on(skill_name) group_left(category) topk by (skill_name) (1, last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\", category=~\"${category:regex}\"}[25h])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{category}}",
          "range": true,
          "instant": false
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(sum by (skill_name) (increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total{skill_name!=\"\", user_email=~\"${user:regex}\"}[$__rate_interval])) unless on(skill_name) last_over_time(skill_meta{job=\"wield\"}[25h]))",
          "legendFormat": "(untracked)",
          "range": true,
          "instant": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
